 the primary and secondary WD\ncomponents of the DWD merger that lead to a post-merger evolution consistent\nwith the observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Aug 2022 18:47:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Nov 2022 16:04:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-21"}
